    description: "Begin a new conversation with the data analyst. Returns a new conversation ID which can be used with the 'messageDataAgent' tool. When messaging with the same conversation ID, the data analyst will remember the context of previous messages. You can start a new conversation at any time, even if you already have an active conversation.",
    inputSchema: z.object({}),
    execute: async () => {
